# 🎲 [AI Truth or Dare Telegram Bot](https://t.me/truth_dare_ai_bot) 🤖

Spice up your Telegram chats instantly! This is a smart party game bot written in Python that uses advanced AI to generate completely unique, hilarious, and unpredictable Truth or Dare prompts on the fly. 

No more recycling the same boring questions—every round is a completely fresh challenge!

👉 **[Click Here to Play Now!](https://t.me/truth_dare_ai_bot)**

---

## 🔥 Key Features

* **🧠 Dynamic AI Generation:** Powered by live AI models to create creative, modern prompts tailored for chat apps (no awkward real-world physical tasks, just pure digital chaos).
* **🚀 System-Wide Inline Mode:** Play with friends anywhere! You don't even need to add the bot to a group chat to use it.
* **📦 Built-in Fallback Pool:** Packed with over 200 hand-crafted, classic Truths and Dares so the game keeps moving instantly even if the network blips.
* **💬 Text & Voice Focused:** Every dare is optimized for modern messaging—expect voice note challenges, emoji-only typing rules, and hilarious text pranks.

---

## 🎮 How to Play

You can experience the game in two different ways depending on how you like to hang out:

### 1. Play Solo or Test Prompts (Direct Message)
1. Open a direct link to the bot: **[@truth_dare_ai_bot](https://t.me/truth_dare_ai_bot)**.
2. Hit `/start` and use the interactive buttons to generate prompts on the fly:
   * **❓ Truth:** Get a deep, hilarious, or slightly embarrassing question you have to answer honestly.
   * **🎲 Dare:** Get a text or voice-note challenge to complete right there.
   * **🔄 Reset Menu:** Head back to the main lobby instructions instantly.

### 2. Play with Friends in ANY Chat (Inline Mode) 🚀
This is the coolest way to play! You can summon the bot inside **any** private DM with a friend, or into any group chat you are already in, without inviting the bot as a member.

1. Open any Telegram chat window.
2. In the text box where you type your messages, type:
   `@truth_dare_ai_bot truth`  or  `@truth_dare_ai_bot dare`
3. A pop-up menu will slide up above your keyboard. 
4. Tap **Share Prompt**, and the bot will instantly inject a fresh, custom AI prompt directly into your conversation!